<br>
Monks get free wipe via fd so throw toy + fd + throw = picked mob. Natural for them.<br>
<br>
If the fd fails oh well drag the monk and res.... they don;t need endurance or mana for more fd's, if you got more than one monk they take over flushing. As for picking, no one on server beats me for sheer pickability but lots of time afk mana &gt; pulling.<br>
<br>
Anyway i pull just fine and no I don;t need to resort to the start stop. I'd love to see it fixed.<br>
<br>
As for my pulling style, if it requires fade to pull off I generally don;t bother unless It's a short run. I find other ways to get the job done.<br>
<br>
Cheers!<br>
